146
00:15:42,639 --> 00:15:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ste u braku?

147
00:15:43,759 --> 00:15:45,120
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo u braku 11.

148
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:45,759
[SPEAKER_02] godina već.

149
00:15:47,759 --> 00:15:49,039
[SPEAKER_02] I to je od početka tako.

150
00:15:50,159 --> 00:15:53,840
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam više tip od bilježnice, a on je više tip od Excel tablice.

151
00:15:56,080 --> 00:16:02,879
[SPEAKER_02] Ali jednostavno, našli smo jedan određeni model i što najbolje u početku našeg braka, samo sam ja radila.

152
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:17,279
